research/history/logs/agent_round_0051.stdout.log:1694:research/history/logs/agent_action_0040_repair_1.json:9:  "self_review": "满足 repair 约束：未改 family_name，未改 env_overrides，仍是相对 r27 只切到 `ARCHITECTURE=two_stage_residual_expert`。根因已确认是 `Unknown architecture`，并已完成 checklist 所需的 whitelist、dispatch、class、exact-string smoke。显式 dispatch smoke 在 `(architecture=two_stage_residual_expert, K=192, EF=1)` 上通过，selection_cost≈0.31x、deployment≈0.19x、total≈0.50x，combined_budget_ratio≈0.33，仍在 LUTurbo 成本硬约束内。override 校验也已通过，下一次真实运行不应再卡在 parse/dispatch 阶段。",
research/history/logs/agent_round_0051.stdout.log:1729:research/history/logs/agent_action_0037_repair_1.json:1:{"change_type":"edit_sae_code","command":"run","family_name":"lowrank_expert_residual","family_stage":"prototype","reference_round":27,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_expert_residual"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","needs_sanity":true,"hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{i∈S_e(x)} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i} + Σ_{j∈T(x)} γ_j(x) c_j。这里 U={u_r} 是静态 low-rank trunk 向量库，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库，C={c_j} 是静态 residual 补偿库；在线侧先计算 trunk 系数 β_r(x)，再用轻量 router 选择单个 expert 子库 e(x) 并在其内做局部 sparse 选择，最后对剩余残差再做一次小预算 sparse 补偿。因此它仍可导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”流水线，兼容性判定为扩展兼容。本次 repair 不改变实验设计，只修复 `lowrank_expert_residual` 的注册链与最小可运行实现，使原始 Round 37 实验能够按原设定重新运行。","summary":"已修复 Round 37 的工程性阻塞：补上 `lowrank_expert_residual` 的 config whitelist、factory dispatch、concrete class，并完成同一目标 `(ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_expert_residual, K=192, EF=1)` 的 instantiate/forward/backward smoke。保持原 family 与 env_overrides 不变，重新运行原始实验。","self_review":"这次 repair 没有改 family_name，也没有改 env_overrides；仍然是相对 r27 只切换到 `ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_expert_residual`。阻塞根因是 `Unknown architecture`，已按架构集成 checklist 修复：whitelist、dispatch、class、exact-string smoke 都已完成。额外把该 family 接到了 `TRUNK_RANK/STAGE1_RATIO` override registry，避免后续调参时静默失效。exact smoke 在 `lowrank_expert_residual, K=192, EF=1` 上通过，估算总成本约 1.06x 原始 matmul、预算比率 0.71x，仍在硬约束内。","next_hypotheses":["如果 rerun 能稳定完成，则再根据真实 FVU 判断 `lowrank + expert + residual` 是否值得继续；当前 repair 轮不对结构优劣做新结论。","如果 rerun 仍失败，下一次 repair 应直接针对新的失败模式处理，而不是再次回到注册链。"],"notes_to_memory":["Round 37 的首个 blocker 是注册链缺失，不是训练语义问题。","`lowrank_expert_residual` 已加入 `sparsify/config.py` whitelist，并加入 `sparsify/sparse_coder.py` dispatch。","已实现最小可运行 `LowRankExpertResidualSparseCoder`：low-rank trunk + expert-local first pass + global residual cleanup second pass。","已补 `research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py` 中 `lowrank_expert_residual -> {TRUNK_RANK, STAGE1_RATIO}`，避免后续 structural override 被拒绝。","exact smoke 结果：`integration_smoke: OK lowrank_expert_residual 192 1 cuda`；成本估算 combined_ratio≈1.06x，combined_budget_ratio≈0.71x，可行。"],"touched_files":["sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py","research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py"]}
research/history/logs/agent_round_0051.stdout.log:1744:research/history/logs/agent_action_0023_repair_1.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"保持原始实验假设不变：最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_{e∈E(x)} Σ_{i∈S_e(x)} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}，prototype 当前固定 |E(x)|=1。在线侧先用轻量 router 选 1 个 expert 子库，再只在该静态子库内做局部 top-k，最后走 LUTurbo/Lottable 的查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿链路，因此兼容性仍为扩展兼容。此次 repair 只修复工程阻塞：补全 `expert_topk` 的 config whitelist、factory dispatch 与最小可训练实现，使原始实验能通过 parse/construct/forward/backward。","summary":"修复 `Unknown architecture: 'expert_topk'` 的注册链阻塞。已在 `sparsify/config.py` 把 `expert_topk` 加入合法 architecture 白名单，在 `sparsify/sparse_coder.py` 增加 `_get_sae_class()` dispatch，并实现最小 `ExpertTopKSparseCoder` 原型；随后用失败时相同的 `architecture=expert_topk, K=64, EF=1` 完成 instantiate/forward/backward smoke test，通过。","change_type":"edit_sae_code","expected_win":"explore_unknown","family_name":"expert_topk","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"这次失败确认为纯注册链 bug，不是 trainer 或优化器问题。repair 后 smoke 已通过，说明 parse/dispatch/forward/backward 链路闭合；如果下一次真实训练仍失败，应按新的失败模式继续修实现，而不是再把问题归因到 architecture 未注册。","needs_sanity":true,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"expert_topk"}],"touched_files":["sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py"],"notes_to_memory":["`expert_topk` 的注册链已补全：config whitelist + `_get_sae_class` dispatch + concrete class。","按架构集成清单对相同失败目标做了 smoke test：`expert_topk`, `K=64`, `EF=1` 已能 instantiate、forward、backward。","smoke 结果的成本估计：selection≈0.06x，deployment≈0.06x，combined≈0.13x；当前 prototype 处于超低成本区。","本轮未新增 tunable 参数，也未改 `research/AutoResearch/` 或 `scripts/`；阻塞不在参数接线。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果真实训练已不再在 parse/dispatch 阶段崩溃，就收集该 prototype 的首个有效 FVU 信号，再决定是否继续该 family。","如果真实训练切换到新的实现级错误，下一轮只修 `expert_topk` 本身，不改实验设计和 env_overrides。"],"reference_round":10}
